other knights - they want to win as much as you do.\n\nYou beat them the king's greatest treasure is yours. And I didn't mean gold.\n\nJOUSTING VR FEATURES\n\n- Physics - experience Exciting fights based on true lance fighting physics.\n- Progression -  Knightly tournaments in which only the best advance to the next stages.\n- Challenge mode -  Smash hanging items. An exceptional aim helps you hit the target.", "short_description": "Welcome to medieval times. Times of Jousting.\nYou take part in a grand tournament competing with other knights, for fame, glory, wealth and to win the king's niece's heart.\n\u201cTo risk life to save a smile on a face of a woman or a child is the secret of chivalry.\u201d"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://vraar.pl/privacy_policy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Vraar S.A.", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://vraar.pl/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "459781504968480"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ARCADE", "CASUAL", "SPORTS"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "743056196616504"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 0, "nodes": []}, "baseline_offer": null, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": []}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "5279537075485442", "version": "1.1"}, "id": "4873104572737866", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_ke